{"tid":320743,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"bu 定 poly 好?","createTime":"2017-07-13T17:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T17:24:00.000Z","uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cadaf79ebf4accf2a78a99f58249ed6c21df215","tid":320743,"uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:43:35.000Z","msg":"bu 文學士定係poly 個文化傳意嗰科好啲? 兩科收分都差唔多，文科好似bu 好啲，但自己又鍾意poly 多啲，求大家俾啲意見。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 4c+1 22分"},{"pid":"6c84a2a79b495a8b27e0b18edf0fd3aaf8dc20cd","tid":320743,"uid":3926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c1252d05aa24f0aa0b700ab2da53a5077d2139b","tid":320743,"uid":91362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"想讀咩major先？"},{"pid":"5a95353e28f97409accbe37605b31ebc17242c8e","tid":320743,"uid":55701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:20:38.000Z","msg":"Bu for sure"},{"pid":"b83650d9765c10680b71c174fe61f777210b9b45","tid":320743,"uid":113457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"poly個科偏culture,translate同communication多<br />\n想讀文學野既就揀bu"},{"pid":"2dd29fd452854b90d1f5bdfb3c33b79b86da5a97","tid":320743,"uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"如果係想讀中文，出黎都係要考返個教學文憑，咁係咪兩間都冇分別?"},{"pid":"87dd49d581f3d84a3f71029a021530a8d579a7b4","tid":320743,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係想讀中文，出黎都係要考返個教學文憑，咁係咪兩間都冇分別?</blockquote><br />\n讀中文考數學做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2ce91152be76a4366cc3328c8e270a11d17956","tid":320743,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係想讀中文，出黎都係要考返個教學文憑，咁係咪兩間都冇分別?</blockquote><br />\n讀中文考數學做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教學文憑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85541898b437c7b4331e46ef8d2d7ffe3b4dac2","tid":320743,"uid":66460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"想讀中文應該去bu"},{"pid":"1d5c74f3f2976e4b7a97c76d7b821e7b626b3642","tid":320743,"uid":24381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"絲打你中英文幾多？"},{"pid":"ed8eb646c609a7a4e4c913aede29dead9ea8df24","tid":320743,"uid":3926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9bf32a6a4e77774518ee286e731f118fc8dee28","tid":320743,"uid":13704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6f721ae4244bd8b79ae3128ddf14b58cb463d97","tid":320743,"uid":53150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bu 文學士定係poly 個文化傳意嗰科好啲? 兩科收分都差唔多，文科好似bu 好啲，但自己又鍾意poly 多啲，求大家俾啲意見。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 4c+1 22分</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想當年我a2 擺bu文學士，a3 就poly文化傳意<br />\n最後入bu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果樓主靜係想讀中文，我睇bu會岩d<br />\n因為當年我上poly個網睇，文化傳意其實有少少偏向翻譯，我當年就係想讀翻譯所以先擺埋poly落a3<br />\n(不過都係勸你打去poly department度問清楚文化傳意係讀d咩，睇下岩唔岩你心水)<br />\n<br />\nbu文學士係冇weight,  只要你夠分(睇樓主個分應該安全，上年好多都係22分) 就算中文冇*都入到<br />\n<br />\nbu文學士就玩聯合收生既，你y1 入到去係未有major, 你讀完year1 就比你揀major<br />\n文學士(我地自己會叫文院) 有6個major可以揀<br />\n中文，英文，翻譯，創意及專業寫作，宗哲，人文學<br />\n係bu文院揀唔揀到你想讀既major係睇gpa<br />\n中文系會睇埋interview, 即係gpa佔50%, interview佔50%<br />\n其他5個major就純睇gpa<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔想唱衰自己間u, 但呢d我覺得你係有必要知<br />\nbu係好好好好好好好好多 GE course(通識課程) <br />\n即係好似中學咁，要讀中英文，數學，IT,歷史，pe, etc<br />\n跟據y1 study schedule, 學校會建議你讀曬以上既GE course<br />\n當然啦，你reg科個陣係可以唔跟佢既，不過如果你唔係y1 讀左佢，你y2 要讀埋major既core就會吃力，隨時讀唔夠credit畢唔到業<br />\n文院人通常最易死就係數學同it,  不過如果你醒醒定定，乖乖地做assignment, 唔識就問prof既話，同埋唔好reg中伏野，通常就唔會爛得去邊，未至於拖低你gpa搞到你揀唔到major既<br />\n<br />\n大學名呢家野，睇你接唔接受到啦，如果你接受唔到都係勸你擺poly<br />\n<br />\n教學文憑呢，我以前有個老師係讀完大學, 先去讀教育文憑，都做到老師，不過呢d問番你中學老師好d<br />\n<br />\npoly真心唔熟，睇下有冇其他巴打答到你啦"},{"pid":"765b7ae0db5b400c00033470e71accf47faebdc3","tid":320743,"uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"最後都係揀咗poly a2, bu a3<br />\n唔該曬各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c364edd071308ccb25c2519955603c6e31b3e3d","tid":320743,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"係poly讀文科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f81bc495acfbc0b8c7d970b46f98a126187de","tid":320743,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"中文一定bu先"}]}